Text: I can't read this. It says "failed to extract page 1, 2 etc" when I open it in comical. Tips on how to read? :(

Well I use comical 0.8 and I can read the files perfectly. If you use an older version of comical, maybe you should download 0.8. Also you can try re-downloading the files. Finally you can use winrar to open the files and see if they are downloaded correctly (If they aren't it will start sending messages).

works fine with cdisplay (v 1.8.1.0 if you need to know).  never have a problem with cdisplay unless the files are corrupt or incomplete - great free reader.
and GIANNIS511, thanks for the ul :)
